{
  "texts": [
    "The current investigation aims at providing explanations for the following research questions:",
    "What are the perceptions of educators regarding the use of these tools and their implications for academic integrity? 2.",
    "What are the current practices of educators in using ChatGPT, DWAs, MTs, and APTs? 3.",
    "What are the policies provided by their institutions and their own suggested policies for the meaningful and ethical use of these tools?",
    "There is already a widespread use of ADWTs that assist educators, learners, and researchers in their tasks even before the release of ChatGPT (Roe et al. 2023; Koh et al. 2022; Roe & Perkins 2022)."
  ]
}